00:03:36.360 --> 00:03:41.460 align:middle line:84%
and evolved and says that our
complete vision of genetics

00:03:41.460 --> 00:03:44.070 align:middle line:84%
and the concept of
DNA controlling life

00:03:44.070 --> 00:03:46.470 align:middle line:90%
is totally false.

00:03:46.470 --> 00:03:51.450 align:middle line:84%
And why this is important is
very simply, all science--

00:03:51.450 --> 00:03:54.690 align:middle line:84%
