00:04:08.860 --> 00:04:11.430 align:middle line:84%
So if you change your
response to the environment,

00:04:11.430 --> 00:04:13.410 align:middle line:84%
change your
environment, then you

00:04:13.410 --> 00:04:16.019 align:middle line:90%
have power over your biology.

00:04:16.019 --> 00:04:17.500 align:middle line:90%
Bottom line is simple.

00:04:17.500 --> 00:04:20.519 align:middle line:84%
We move from victim
biology genetics

00:04:20.519 --> 00:04:24.000 align:middle line:84%
to master of
